OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with outbreaks of light
OL,6,Frain during Sunday morning. Becoming
OL,7,Flargely dry with variable amounts of
OL,8,Fcloud and occasional brighter spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping into the afternoon. Windy
OL,10,Falong the coast. Mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry with variable amounts of
OL,13,Fcloud and clear spells overnight. It
OL,14,Fwill remain on the breezy side,
OL,15,Fespecially along coasts. A mild night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
