OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FStaying dry with variable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud during Monday
OL,7,Fmorning. However, increasing amounts
OL,8,Fof sunshine are likely to develop into
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Rather mild, with
OL,10,Flighter winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,13,FLargely dry with variable amounts of
OL,14,Fcloud and bright or sunny spells
OL,15,FTuesday. Dry and bright with sunny
OL,16,Fspells Wednesday and Thursday. Rather
OL,17,Fmild, with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
